### Chapter 2 Sources (Notes 1–78)
*The Habsburg Bid for Mastery, 1519–1659*

**Military history foundations:**

- **C. Oman**, *A History of the Art of War in the Sixteenth Century*
  (1937) — Kennedy calls this "the best military narrative for
  this period"
- **G. R. Elton**, *Reformation Europe 1517–1559*
